0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:03:40.000Z","msg":"出面見到幾個post 啲所謂前線既細路啲語氣都好嚇人<br />\n甚至有啲係到屌鳩人淨係買乾糧比佢地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己上咁多次前線其實根本唔會有心機諗食咩<br />\n就算真係餓 見到有啲方包排包傳緊 攞一片食就已經夠<br />\n班細路要認清打緊仗唔係嘆緊世界<br />\n就算真係想食好啲都唔該態度好啲 唔好屌鳩人地一片好心送乾糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84330e2429c254c85d69242c38b1c3c96f9fef3b","tid":1385441,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44eb477c31a4ed3a92e6a3e76de91a2f4e70202a","tid":1385441,"uid":5199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:03:40.000Z","msg":"出面見到幾個post 啲所謂前線既細路啲語氣都好嚇人<br />\n甚至有啲係到屌鳩人淨係買乾糧比佢地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己上咁多次前線其實根本唔會有心機諗食咩<br />\n就算真係餓 見到有啲方包排包傳緊 攞一片食就已經夠<br />\n班細路要認清打緊仗唔係嘆緊世界<br />\n就算真係想食好啲都唔該態度好啲 唔好屌鳩人地一片好心送乾糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"所以咪要將focus轉落買gear到<br />\ngear差極都有用"},{"pid":"b8f8a5bc7e91c4cc5b95de83ef62040bc42c0c30","tid":1385441,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6fb4885939831bd9af28efc868616df0f6d55f8","tid":1385441,"uid":280772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:46:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2985cd54bb6dc9471c8575a75a7c2c8d2722f2cf","tid":1385441,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b33e9229c54132b29122517271536192d45bc27","tid":1385441,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"講講下 又好似係...."},{"pid":"c4d2cd6c32d9dfaec9df2fc679e2f10934686b26","tid":1385441,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2985cd54bb6dc9471c8575a75a7c2c8d2722f2cf","tid":1385441,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:46:59.